Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa{\i0}
